Package: RSimpleFFI
Version: 1.0.1.9000
Title: Simple Foreign Function Interface using 'S7' and 'libffi'
Description: Simple Foreign Function Interface for 'R' using 'libffi' and 'S7' classes.
    Supports calling 'C' functions with type conversion and struct handling.
    Includes standard 'C' types (int8, int16, int32, int64, uint variants), platform
    types (size_t, bool), floating point types, and complex struct types.
    Experimental header parsing using 'tinycc' as `C` preprocessor enables automatic generation of 'R' 
    bindings from 'C' header files, simplifying package development for 'C' libraries.
